    <h1>Bienvenidos a Expresiones Mexicanos. This is a collection of all those crazy mexican expressions we grew up hearing. I got the idea to do this when I was at a party and some friends could not stop cracking up at all the expressions. I hope you enjoy :) </h1>
    
    <!-- list -->
    <ul class="dichos">
        <% for(let i = 0; i < dichos.length; i++){ %>
            <li class="dicho">
                <span><%= dichos[i].dicho %></span>
                <span><%= dichos[i].literal %></span>
                <span><%= dichos[i].actual %></span>
            </li>
        <% } %>
    </ul>

